  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/3e0cb00448229c32d52c522656e03d82.avif?t=1766128168\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pachillinko is a mix of japanese Pachinko and western Plinko style game, set in neon synthwave design with some retro feeling of 80s. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing mouse-only clicking gameplay allows you to sit back and just chill... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game features:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Pachinko game mode</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Plinko game mode</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Spinning slot wheel for extra cash</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Incremental progression</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Relaxing synthwave music</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Great mix of idle and active gameplay</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Neon cyberpunk visuals</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Rhytm based special visual effects</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Total chill</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Total relax</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/f9fcc6bb1402e3b7afa01fb0832c9fc4.poster.avif?t=1766128168\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/f9fcc6bb1402e3b7afa01fb0832c9fc4.webm?t=1766128168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/f9fcc6bb1402e3b7afa01fb0832c9fc4.mp4?t=1766128168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/0ec13a824662586dc7a500cff0666db7.poster.avif?t=1766128168\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/0ec13a824662586dc7a500cff0666db7.webm?t=1766128168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/0ec13a824662586dc7a500cff0666db7.mp4?t=1766128168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/f408d549d5e5abec4947b5e636e93572.avif?t=1766128168\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/3e0cb00448229c32d52c522656e03d82.avif?t=1766128168\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pachillinko is a mix of japanese Pachinko and western Plinko style game, set in neon synthwave design with some retro feeling of 80s. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing mouse-only clicking gameplay allows you to sit back and just chill... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game features:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Pachinko game mode</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Plinko game mode</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Spinning slot wheel for extra cash</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Incremental progression</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Relaxing synthwave music</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Great mix of idle and active gameplay</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Neon cyberpunk visuals</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Rhytm based special visual effects</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Total chill</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>- Total relax</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/f9fcc6bb1402e3b7afa01fb0832c9fc4.poster.avif?t=1766128168\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855270/extras/f9fcc6bb1402e3b7afa01fb0832c9fc4.webm?t=1766128168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akam